data.description: Welcome to this lovely one-owner home situated in the popular Holt Park community! This 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home is one of the largest floorplans in the neighborhood w/1884 sq ft of living space. The inviting main level features a spacious family room, well-appointed kitchen with S/S appliances & breakfast bar/eating area, a handy first-floor laundry & half bath. Upstairs hosts the updated primary suite complete w/full bath with tub & shower, two additional bedrooms, and a second full bath. Many recent updates including newer HVAC, water heater, appliances, flooring, garage door opener, and much more. Charming covered frt porch and rear patio with pergola. Oversized two car garage with large space above perfect for finishing. Community has a clubhouse, pool, wkout facility, & playground.
